{"type": "article", "id": 28152, "title": "昼夜挂钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-14T06:42:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 204, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171439w2dRS7QhofTFMbKV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>飞速流逝的时间用黑白的昼夜变化来体现会是什么样？美国设计师 Dan Taylor 以电子纸（E-paper）作为钟面设计了一款黑白两色的挂钟 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/37577539/Circadian-Clock\">Circadian Clock</a>，不断变化的白色（上午）或者黑色（下午）面积代替了时针，分针也会根据钟面底色的不同自动变化颜色。目前它还是一款概念产品，尚未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070217143760YRJNcMvqFDBZ5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171437QM6m4hbBe2q3nOGU.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171438eac3tx4h9oDsw0gA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171439Xk3CEZdReqrW4Oa9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}